- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is the most likely category as the paper deals with algorithms for vertex enumeration of polytopes in 2D projection, which is a common problem in computational geometry. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper proposes an algorithm for efficient vertex enumeration. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is another possible category as the paper deals with polytopes, which are objects of study in discrete mathematics. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is a possible category as the paper mentions the complexity of the algorithm and its empirical performance, which are related to numerical analysis. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on the theoretical complexity of the problem, but rather on proposing an efficient algorithm.
